                Get early access
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3 sm:mt-0 sm:ml-3">
              <a href="/demo" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base leading-6 font-medium rounded-md text-aquamarine-700 bg-aquamarine-100 hover:text-aquamarine-600 hover:bg-aquamarine-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:border-aquamarine-300 transition duration-150 ease-in-out md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10">
